  "text": "The results of the study [CITATION_1] state that field selection is directly influenced by students' future goals, their courses are successful, family expectations and their interests and skills. It was observed that gender and age variables of students did not make a significant difference in results. In addition, it has been determined that the economic level of the student's family and the preferences of closest friends do not have the expected effect in field selection, but rather that individual expectations have a guiding function.",
